.DT
bury
$MUDNAME$ player help
bury

.SH Name
.SI 5
bury - Tidy up the place
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
bury [items]
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command will tidy the place up by burying stuff that you list.  It gives
a few guild points to you for being such a good citizen.  If you don't specify
something to bury, all stuff littering the floor around you will be buried.

The command 'recover' will allow you to recover stuff that was recently
buried.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> bury corpse
You tidy up the place, clearing away a corpse of a bodyguard.
.EI

.SH See Also
.SP 5 5
recover
.EP
